tem\nmodeling interacting phototactic cells. The simulations of our model are\nconsistent with experimentally observed phototactic motion. (C) 2012\nElsevier Ltd. All rights reserved.', 'cited-references': 'Alber Mark S., 2002, MATH SYST THEORY, V134, P1.\nAOKI I, 1982, B JPN SOC SCI FISH, V48, P1081.\nBhaya D, 2008, HYPERBOLIC PROBLEMS: THEORY, NUMERICS, APPLICATIONS, P145, DOI 10.1007/978-3-540-75712-2\\_12.\nBhaya D, 2004, MOL MICROBIOL, V53, P745, DOI 10.1111/j.1365-2958.2004.04160.x.\nBhaya D, 2001, P NATL ACAD SCI USA, V98, P7540, DOI 10.1073/pnas.131201098.\nBhaya D, 2001, J BACTERIOL, V183, P6140, DOI 10.1128/JB.183.20.6140-6143.2001.\nBhaya D, 2006, J BACTERIOL, V188, P7306, DOI 10.1128/JB.00573-06.\nBhaya D, 1999, P NATL ACAD SCI USA, V96, P3188, DOI 10.1073/pnas.96.6.3188.\nBURKART U, 1980, J MATH BIOL, V10, P257, DOI 10.1007/BF00276985.\nBurriesci M, 2008, J PHOTOCH PHOTOBIO B, V91, P77, DOI 10.1016/j.jphotobiol.2008.01.012.\nCouzin ID, 2002, J THEOR BIOL, V218, P1, DOI 10.1006/yjtbi.3065.\nCucker F, 2007, JPN J MATH, V2, P197, DOI 10.1007/s11537-007-0647-x.\nCucker F, 2007, IEEE T AUTOMAT CONTR, V52, P852, DOI 10.1109/TAC.2007.895842.\nDegond P, 2008, MATH MOD METH APPL S, V18, P1193, DOI 10.1142/S0218202508003005.\nFatehi H, 2010, MATH MED BIOL, V27, P373, DOI 10.1093/imammb/dqq002.\nGalante A., 2011, UNIFYING THEMES COMP, V8, P105.\nHa SY, 2009, DISCRETE CONT DYN-B, V12, P77, DOI 10.3934/dcdsb.2009.12.77.\nHa SY, 2009, COMMUN MATH SCI, V7, P453.\nHa SY, 2008, KINET RELAT MOD, V1, P415.\nHillen T, 2009, J MATH BIOL, V58, P183, DOI 10.1007/s00285-008-0201-3.\nHorstmann D, 2003, JAHRESBER DTSCH MATH, V105, P103.\nHUTH A, 1992, J THEOR BIOL, V156, P365, DOI 10.1016/S0022-5193(05)80681-2.\nIkeuchi M, 2008, PHOTOCH PHOTOBIO SCI, V7, P1159, DOI 10.1039/b802660m.\nKaiser D, 2008, ANNU REV GENET, V42, P109, DOI 10.1146/annurev.genet.42.110807.091615.\nKatz Y, 2011, P NATL ACAD SCI USA, V108, P18720, DOI 10.1073/pnas.1107583108.\nKELLER EF, 1971, J THEOR BIOL, 